OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSainsbury's urged to up pay
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto match cost of living    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A group of major investors is calling  
OL,6, on Sainsbury's to commit to paying all 
OL,7, its workers the Real Living Wage to    
OL,8, tackle the rising cost of living.      
OL,10,FThe Real Living Wage aims to ensure    
OL,11,Fwages cover everyday needs and is      
OL,12,Fvoluntarily paid by around 9,500 firms.
OL,14,FIt is higher than the compulsory       
OL,15,Fnational minimum wage.                 
OL,17,FSainsbury's staff in inner London and  
OL,18,Foutside the capital are now paid the   
OL,19,FReal Living Wage but staff in outer    
OL,20,FLondon are not.                        
